body.section:
The default implementation provides an implementation for the TabbedContentManagerUI and for the DesktopContentManagerUI.
To obtain an instance use the following (for example):
import org.noos.xing.mydoggy.plaf.ui.content.desktop; ... ContentManagerUI contentManagerUI = new MyDoggyDesktopContentManagerUI();
or import org.noos.xing.mydoggy.plaf.ui.content.tabbed; ... ContentManagerUI contentManagerUI = new MyDoggyTabbedContentManagerUI();
If you want to implement your own ContentManageUI, your class must implement non only the ContentManageUI interface but also the BackContentManagerUI interface in the package org.noos.xing.mydoggy.plaf.ui.content..
This is to provide all neccesary methods to use the manager.
